5. Non-Thermal UV-C Sanitization DetailObjective: Complete destruction of food-borne pathogens (e.g., E. coli) without heating the fertilizer or altering organic nutrient profiles.Core Pipe Component: 5-foot section of clear quartz glass (fused silica) ensuring 90%+ UV-C light wave penetration into the moving liquid.Housing Enclosure: Sealed, highly reflective aluminum cylinder lining the quartz glass.Light Array: 254nm wavelength UV-C LED strips mounted internally facing the tube for 360-degree radiation coverage.Safety Restriction: Misting systems inside structural airlocks must strictly use pure water or air curtains instead of essential oils to prevent killing beneficial colony insects (ladybugs/lacewings).
